But what do skeptics like me know?
Twitch has 55 million unique visitors per month, and it is the fourth largest source of peak internet traffic.
How is Amazon going to do that?
It’s hard to imagine Twitch turning into Amazon Instant Video as gracefully as YouTube could just absorb Twitch.
However, Twitch has something that any company would love to have: the crowds of young men that advertisers dream of.
Amazon and Twitch both believe in the future of gaming, and the channel is showing no signs of fading, even as a spectacular sport.
